altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 28
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 28
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v28 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Chicken Little, The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Mario Superstar Baseball, Geist, and Resident Evil 4. The disc also features videos of the following: The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess, Killer 7, Battalion Wars, Mario Superstar Baseball, Geist, Medal of Honor: European Assault, The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Charlie and the Chocolate Factory, Chicken Little, Madden NFL 06, Fantastic 4, WWE Day of Reckoning 2, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
